                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Sustainability is a core part of what we do. Our EcoSoft™ and EcoLite™ fabrics are made from recycled materials. We're continuously working to reduce our environmental footprint across packaging, production, and supply chain.</p>",
